flowchart TD
    A([Start overlaps(interval)]) --> B[thisStart=getStartMillis; thisEnd=getEndMillis]
    B --> C{interval == null?}
    C -- Yes --> D[now=currentTimeMillis]
    D --> E{return thisStart < now AND now < thisEnd}
    C -- No --> F[otherStart=interval.getStartMillis; otherEnd=interval.getEndMillis]
    F --> G{return thisStart < otherEnd AND otherStart < thisEnd}
    E --> H([End])
    G --> H
